Available Tools: send_email | compose_draft | send_reply | forward_email
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": ["string"], "cc": ["string"], "subject": "string", "body": "string", "attachments": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "status": "sent|draft|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Send the weekly status report to the project team.
Call: { "func_call": "send_email", "to": ["j.miller@techcorp.com", "s.lee@techcorp.com"], "cc": ["manager@techcorp.com"], "subject": "Weekly Status Update - Oct 24", "body": "Hi team,\n\nAttached is the weekly status report for the Phoenix project. Please review before our Monday meeting.\n\nBest,\nAlex", "attachments": ["weekly_status_oct24.pdf"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_89234a", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T14:30:00Z" }

Question: Draft an email to the vendor asking for a price quote on new servers.
Call: { "func_call": "compose_draft", "to": ["sales@cloudinfra.net"], "cc": [], "subject": "RFQ: Enterprise Server Cluster", "body": "Hello,\n\nWe are looking to purchase a new server cluster. Could you please provide a quote for 5 units of model X-900 with 128GB RAM?\n\nRegards,\nDavid Chen", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "draft_11209b", "status": "draft", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T15:12:45Z" }

Question: Reply to Sarah confirming the meeting time for tomorrow.
Call: { "func_call": "send_reply", "to": ["sarah.j@designstudio.io"], "cc": [], "subject": "Re: Design Review Meeting", "body": "Hi Sarah,\n\nYes, 2 PM tomorrow works perfectly for me. I'll send the calendar invite shortly.\n\nThanks,\nMike", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_9921c", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T16:05:22Z" }

Question: Forward the client feedback document to the product team with a note.
Call: { "func_call": "forward_email", "to": ["product-team@mycompany.com"], "cc": ["lead@mycompany.com"], "subject": "Fwd: Client Feedback - Q3", "body": "Team,\n\nPlease see the attached feedback from our key client. We need to discuss these points in the next sprint planning.\n\nThanks,\nEmma", "attachments": ["client_feedback_q3.docx"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_7732d", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T16:45:10Z" }

Question: Send an invoice to the billing department.
Call: { "func_call": "send_email", "to": ["billing@vendor.com"], "cc": ["accounts@mycompany.com"], "subject": "Invoice #4022 - October Services", "body": "Please find attached invoice #4022 for October consulting services. Payment terms are Net 30.\n\nBest regards,\nFinance Dept", "attachments": ["invoice_4022.pdf"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_3341e", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T09:15:33Z" }

Question: Compose a draft invitation for the holiday party.
Call: { "func_call": "compose_draft", "to": ["all-staff@mycompany.com"], "cc": [], "subject": "You're Invited: Annual Holiday Party!", "body": "Hi Everyone,\n\nJoin us for our annual holiday party on December 15th at the Grand Hotel. More details to follow!\n\nCheers,\nHR Team", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "draft_5562f", "status": "draft", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T11:20:00Z" }

Question: Reply to the support ticket confirming the issue is resolved.
Call: { "func_call": "send_reply", "to": ["user123@example.com"], "cc": ["support-lead@mycompany.com"], "subject": "Re: Ticket #9981 - Login Issue", "body": "Hello,\n\nWe have applied the patch and verified that your login issue is now resolved. Please try again and let us know if you encounter any further problems.\n\nBest,\nSupport Team", "attachments": [] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_6673g", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-24T13:40:15Z" }

Question: Send the signed contract to the legal team.
